                     <note>
                        (fol. 1) Beg. imperf.: 'For þe mar devocion þarin suld be' (1. 178: see beginning
                        of poem pr. J. Ullman, 'Studien zu Richard Rolle de Hampole', <title>Englische
                        Studien</title> 7 (1884), 470), ends imperf. (fol. 79v): 'þare fore lewed men haf greet
